de: Supplemental Contribution Amendment to the Administration Agreement between Switzerland, acting through the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (formerly known as the Swiss Federal Department of Eonomic Affairs) and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the Multi-Donor Trust Fund for Middle Income Countries for Financial Sector Reform and Strengthening Initiative (TF No. 070723)   - 11-12-2012 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, der IBRD und der IDA über den Treuhandfonds zur Reform und Stärkung des Finanzsektors (FIRST) in Ländern mit mittlerem Einkommen (TF No 070723)
